article_title: Obamacare Ushers In Pile Of New 2014 Tax Forms

article_metadata.author: Great Speculations

og.description: The Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act, also known as Obamacare, was enacted in 2012 has taken several years to implement and phase in. Now that the Obamacare 2014 individual health insurance mandate is in effect, many taxpayers will face confusion over tax penalties, exemptions, premium tax credits, claw backs [...]
